Author: Russ Grimmett

Author: RJP MWTK
Body: I like the game, but please update the app. Its current version does not support Android 9.

Author: N.R. Dickson
Body: Love the game. I never get tired of playing it. However, I'd give it five stars if Android would get the update  that Apple got last year. Would love to have the new aliens and especially the flame thrower. Please update it for the rest of us. Great game.

Author: A Google User
Subject: Klassic Kochalka
Body: Fantastic goofy way to kill time. The power ups never get old, and the challenges are just inane enough to keep you on your toes. Best played while listening to James Kochalka Superstar, of course.

Author: A Google User
Subject: Kochalka quality!!!!
Body: This game is out of sight!!! Super addicting and totally rad artwork and game play!!! Essential.

Author: A Google User
Subject: Cool game
Body: Runs poorly on my Nexus 10, which is OK cuz most new games are running slow on this old thing. Pixeljam + Kochalka = Amazing

Author: Googleユーザー
Subject: チャーミングでPOP
Body: チャーミングでPOPなデザインと、ギャラガのようなゲームスタイルで、魅力ある作品。チマチマと敵を潰していく楽しさと、敵の弾丸を避ける楽しさがある。残念な点は、火力不足となることが多い。ギャラガ独自の、敵を上手く倒すテクニックを磨くゲームスタンスは感じられないところ。パワーアップアイテムのコンボが成り立てば、スコアを稼げるが、運ゲーと化しているところが見受けられる。

Author: A Google User
Subject: A total romp
Body: Great gameplay, solid controls, a great shoot-and-collect flow and lots of weapons and powerups, no in app purchases or ads, fun sound and graphics. Perfect arcade game!

Author: A Google User
Subject: Galaga Reboot
Body: If you're played Galaga (which is like Space Invaders) then you know the general gameplay. The aesthetics are nice and fun, and the game is entertaining.
